Title: PostgreSQL database and sessions (Linux, Windows): default postgres installation will be detected automatically
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1611234916
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

The default postgres installation database for Linux and Windows can be monitored simply by
adding the rule "PostgreSQL database and sessions (Linux, Windows)" to the agent.

For monitoring custom postgres installations or multiple postgres instances manual configuration is still required.
